                        <div class="row" id="Maharaparaj" tabindex="1" style="outline:none;">
                            <h4 style="color: #337ab7">MAHARAJ SAHEB</h4>
                            &emsp;&emsp;Maharaj Saheb was the third Sant Sat Guru of Radhasoami Faith. He was born in
                            Piyari Kalan, Kabir Chaura, Varanasi,
                            on Thursday, the 28<sup>th</sup> March 1861. Maharaj Saheb's name was Brahm Shankar. Huzur
                            Maharaj had given Maharaj Saheb the Parmarthi name 'Premanand'.
                            <a id="readmor3" onclick="functionexpand3()" style="cursor: pointer">
                                <u>Read More..</u>
                            </a>
